OL,7,FSentencing Abbkr, who has paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenia and believed people
OL,9,Fpossessed by evil spirits were
OL,10,Fcontrolling him, Judge Melbourne Inman
OL,11,FKC said: "I am satisfied you committed
OL,12,Fboth of these offences while suffering
OL,13,Fwith a severe mental illness. It is
OL,14,Fclear from the evidence that neither
OL,15,Fyou nor anyone else had any insight
OL,16,Finto the illness you were developing.
OL,18,F"You were not therefore being treated,
OL,19,Fyou did not accelerate your illness
OL,20,Fthrough alcohol or drugs.
