OL,7,F"It is clear beyond doubt that you
OL,8,Frepresent a very great danger to
OL,9,Fmembers of the public.
OL,11,F"On the basis of the evidence before
OL,12,Fme it is highly likely you will
OL,13,Frequire life-long treatment for this
OL,14,Fillness.
OL,16,F"If you were transferred to prison
OL,17,Fthere would be a significant risk of
OL,18,Fyou relapsing, and being a danger to
OL,19,Fothers including staff.
